initial_assets.description: BTC is a derivative that tracks the real value of 1 Bitcoin - https://bitcoin.org. It is 100% decentralized asset, backed 1:1 by real BTC and can be deposited or withdrawn using a gateway service.

LTC is a derivative that tracks the real value of 1 Litecoin - https://litecoin.com It is 100% decentralized asset, backed 1:1 by real LTC and can be deposited or withdrawn using bridge or gateway services.

ETH is a derivative that tracks the real value of 1 Ethereum - https://www.ethereum.org. It is 100% decentralized asset, backed 1:1 by real ETH and can be deposited or withdrawn using bridge or gateway services.

DASH is a derivative that tracks the real value of 1 Dashcoin - http://dashcoin.info. It is 100% decentralized asset, backed 1:1 by real DSH and can be deposited or withdrawn using bridge or gateway services.
